//www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2897277223911398654/comments/default/5419746586479985292?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/01/Security-Guide-for-Political-Activists.html?showComment=1549263611488#c5419746586479985292","title":"为啥朝廷总抓不到俺&#8212;&#8212;十年反党活动的安全经验汇总"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2897277223911398654/comments/default/4258547668949810982?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/01/Security-Guide-for-Political-Activists.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2897277223911398654","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/2897277223911398654","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2019年2月4日 15:00:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"C0UNRns_cSp7ImA9WhBREUw.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2525676314404947903"},"published":{"$t":"2013-03-01T12:14:57.549+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2013-03-01T12:14:57.549+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2013-03-01T12:14:57.549+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 李四\n博文中的图片看不到，有可能是因为你用 GoAgent 翻墙。\n其实直接在 Google ..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 李四<br />博文中的图片看不到，有可能是因为你用 GoAgent 翻墙。<br />其实直接在 Google Reader 里面看俺的博文，无需翻墙软件，就可以看到全文（包括图片）<br />提醒一下：<br />用加密的【HTTPS】方式访问 Google Reader，可以避免 GFW 的敏感词过滤，起到翻墙的效果。<br />[url]https://www.google.com/reader/[/url]<br /><br />反复刷新的问题，有可能是你的浏览器禁用了 cookie<br />"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8013463250830849786/comments/default/2525676314404947903?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8013463250830849786/comments/default/2525676314404947903?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/02/film-soviet-story.html?showComment=1362111297549#c2525676314404947903","title":"影评&#65306;&#12298;苏维埃往事&#12299;&#8212;&#8212;帮你看清苏联和纳粹的共同本质"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/8013463250830849786/comments/default/7363701795265505846?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/02/film-soviet-story.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-8013463250830849786","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/8013463250830849786","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2013年3月1日 12:14:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"CUEGQ3s6eyp7ImA9WhBQE04.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1820943734409731481"},"published":{"$t":"2013-03-15T15:47:02.513+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2013-03-15T15:47:02.513+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2013-03-15T15:47:02.513+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"再来说说民间运动的“结构性”和“组织化”\n通常大家以为，规模越大的民间运动，就越需要组织化。\n其实不..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"再来说说民间运动的“结构性”和“组织化”<br />通常大家以为，规模越大的民间运动，就越需要组织化。<br />其实不一定。<br /><br />有些时候，外部环境持续发酵，会让某个社会群体的情绪处于某种临界状态。<br />然后某个很小的事件充当引爆点，整个群体情绪就爆发出来。<br />全过程中，并不需要有一个严密的组织来领导和协调。<br />当年的六四学生运动，有点类似这个情形——并没有严密的幕后组织者。<br />印尼的学生运动，也类似这个情形。<br /><br />另外，推荐看一本比较经典的心理学著作《乌合之众——大众心理研究》<br />在[url=https://code.google.com/p/program-think/wiki/Books]俺的网盘[/url]上分享过<br />"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2263087291505131273/comments/default/1820943734409731481?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2263087291505131273/comments/default/1820943734409731481?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/08/revolution-6.html?showComment=1363333622513#c1820943734409731481","title":"谈革命[6]&#65306;回顾&#8220;最近50年的革命史&#8221;"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2263087291505131273/comments/default/2949424900211913736?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/08/revolution-6.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2263087291505131273","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/2263087291505131273","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2013年3月15日 15:47:00"}]},{"gd$eta